file.name: NotificationMbox.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
NotificationMbox:
  type: object
  properties:
    name:
      type: string
      maxLength: 250
      description: |
        Mbox name.
        Validation
          * No blank values allowed.
          * A '-clicked' suffix or the following names are not allowed for mbox names: ** display mboxes **, ** any mbox **, ** click from display mbox **
          * Allowed chars: - '-, ./=`:;&!@#$%^&*()+|?~[]{}'
    state:
      type: string
      description: Mbox state token
